RvaFileMap::MapElement

RvaFileMap::MapElement Class Reference

#include <RvaFileMap.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

An RvaFileMap is composed of zero or more MapElements. Each MapElement describes the mapping from some contiguous relative virtual address space to some contiguous region of the file.
